to compile this you need:
  python libs:
    kivy 1.10.0
    pygame
    cython 0.24.1
    jnius
    python3crystax
  apt packages:
    openjdk-8-jre
    openjdk-8-jdk-headless or openjdk-8-jdk

if using a different version of openjdk, you will have to change the second
line in main.py to the correct java_home path

configure python3crystax install folder in buildozer.spec
download here https://www.crystax.net/en/download

see buildozer python3 install for more info
https://github.com/kivy/buildozer
